longBusinessSummary: Eagle Ford Oil & Gas Corp., an independent oil and gas company, is engaged in the exploration, development, and production of oil and gas properties in the Texas and Louisiana-Gulf Coast Region. It has interests in various wells, including Vick 2 and Alexander 1 wells in Lee County, Texas; and East Pearsall well in Frio County, Texas. The company has a gas pipeline of approximately 13 miles in Jefferson and Harrison Counties, Ohio. Eagle Ford Oil & Gas Corp. is based in Houston, Texas.
